Michael Long (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Long_(actor) 0 Michael Long (1947 in Sydney, Australia – 1991 in Australia) was an Australian actor, best known for his television work. he appeared in ealy roles Matlock Police, Homicide, Division 4, Bluey His TV credits include: Cop Shop, Prisoner (as Mick O'Brien), Taurus Rising (as Sam Farrer), Sons and Daughters (as Stephen Morrell) and Richmond Hill (as Craig Connors). He appeared in the Australian film Careful, He Might Hear You Long died of lung cancer in 1991 at the age of 44 Michael_Long ( 1947 in Sydney , Australia – 1991 in Australia ) was an_Australian_actor , best_known for his_television_work . he appeared in ealy_roles_Matlock_Police , Homicide , Division_4 , Bluey His_TV_credits include : Cop_Shop , Prisoner_( as Mick_O'Brien_) , Taurus Rising ( as Sam_Farrer_)_,_Sons_and_Daughters_( as Stephen_Morrell ) and Richmond_Hill_( as Craig_Connors_) .
